The Ona of Abaji and Chairman of the FCT Council of Traditional Rulers, His Royal Majesty (HRM), Alhaji Adamu Baba Yunusa, has urged the APC chairmanship candidate in the February 12, 2022, council election in the area, Alhaji Mohammed Angulu Loko, to ensure he and his supporters maintain peace before, during and after the election. Alhaji Yunusa, who made the call when he received the APC chairmanship candidate and some party executives at his palace on Thursday, said if the emergence of the APC chairmanship candidate was the best for the council, he prayed for God to let it be.  